        dc:description           "FIGURES 57–62. Phalangopsis ferratilis n. sp. Phallic sclerite of paratype ♂ (ISLA 65757). 57—dorsal view; 58—ventral view; 59—lateral view; 60—frontal view; 61—endophallic sclerite in dorsal, lateral and ventral view, respectively. 62—copulatory papilla of paratype ♀ (ISLA 65755). a—dorsal view; b—lateral view; c—ventral view. Abbreviations: Ps.db, psudepiphallic dorsal branch; Ps.P1, pseudepiphallic paramere 1; Ps.P2, pseudepiphallic paramere 2; Ps.m.l, pseudepiphallic median lobes; A, sclerite A; Ps.arm, pseudepiphallic arm; Ps.b, pseudepiphallic branch; Ect.ap, ectophallic apodeme; Ect.lb, ectophallic lateral bar; Ect.mp, ectophallic median portion; Ect.arc, ectophallic arc; End, endophallus; End.d, endophallic distal portion; End.mp, endophallic median portion; End.ap, endophallic apodeme." ;
